## Pre-requisites
Download and unzip the project
Please, ensure you have 'Node Js' and cypress installed in your machine

## Installation
Install cypress with: npm install cypress --save-dev
Install project dependencies with: npm i

## Running the test: 
 - Open the terminal and run: npx cypress open (select appropriate browser and feature file to execute)
 - Open the terminal and run: npx cypress run (To run test in headless mode)

## Viewing report after headless execution: 
 - Navigate to ./cypress/reports/html and open index.html